@startuml
title Viaverse Media Upload / CDN / Moderation — Activity Diagram
start
:User selects media;
:Request upload session;
:Validate context/type/size and user permission;
if (Allowed?) then (yes)
  :Generate presigned URL;
  :Create MediaAsset(PENDING);
  :Client uploads directly to S3;
  :Confirm upload;
  :Processing job\nEXIF strip / thumbnail / transcode;
  :Moderation scan;
  if (Safe?) then (yes)
    :Set APPROVED;
    :Attach to domain context;
    :Generate delivery URL\npublic/signed policy;
    :Emit MediaApproved;
  else (no)
    :Set REJECTED;
    :Emit MediaRejected;
  endif
else (no)
  :Reject upload request;
endif
stop

note bottom
Original objects stay private.
Public profile assets may be public/CDN,
private chat/job assets use signed access.
end note
@enduml
